content: calintje: Merged a single substantial PR #2136 implementing Solana web3.js V2 and automated liquidity providing on Orca, which involved massive code changes (+352,169/-72,449 lines) across 3,574 files. Activity was occasional throughout the month, with contributions on 8 days and 25 commits primarily focused on configuration (50%) and code (42%) changes. The PR took 361 hours to merge and represented a significant feature addition to the project.
